{"title_page": "Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual jumping", "text_new": "{{short description|Equestrian at the Olympics}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Individual jumping\n|games = 1924 Summer\n|image = \n|caption = \n|venue = [[Stade Olympique Yves-du-Manoir]]\n|date = 27 July\n|competitors = 43\n|nations = 11\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Alphonse Gemuseus]]\n|goldNOC = SUI\n|silver = [[Tommaso Lequio di Assaba]]\n|silverNOC = ITA\n|bronze = [[Adam Kr\u00f3likiewicz]]\n|bronzeNOC = POL\n|prev = [[Equestrian at the 1920 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual jumping|1920]]\n|next = [[Equestrian at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual jumping|1928]]\n}}\n{{EquestrianAt1924SummerOlympics}}\n\nThe individual jumping was one of five [[equestrianism]] events on the [[Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics]] programme.\n\nThe competition was held on Saturday 27 July 1924. 43 riders from 11 nations competed.\n\n==Results==\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n! Place || Rider || Faults || Time\n|-\n| {{gold1}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Alphonse Gemuseus]]|SUI|1924 Summer}} || 6.00 || 2:24.4\n|-\n| {{silver2}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Tommaso Lequio di Assaba]]|ITA|1924 Summer}} || 8.75 || 2:42.0\n|-\n| {{Bronze3}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Adam Kr\u00f3likiewicz]]|POL|1924 Summer}} || 10.00 || 2:38.4\n|-\n| 4 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Philip Bowden-Smith]]|GBR|1924 Summer}} || 10.50 || 2:41.4\n|-\n| 5 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[An\u00edbal de Almeida]]|POR|1924 Summer}} || 12.00 || 2:28.8\n|-\n| 6 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[\u00c5ke Thelning]]|SWE|1924 Summer}} || 12.00 || 2:30.4\n|-\n| 7 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Axel St\u00e5hle]]|SWE|1924 Summer}} || 12.25 || 2:40.0\n|-\n| 8 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Nicolas LeRoy]]|BEL|1924 Summer}} || 14.75 || 2:42.2\n|-\n| 9 ||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Jos\u00e9 \u00c1lvarez de Boh\u00f3rquez|Jos\u